Plus, fingerprint resistant stainless steel keeps this fridges looking great. Inside this 21 cu. ft. model you'll also find the BRIGHT SERIES LED lighting. It casts a bright, white light and uses less energy than incandescent bulbs.

300015404.Title: Maytag 21 cu. ft. Top Freezer Refrigerator in Fingerprint Resistant Stainless Steel
300015404.Description: Maytag top-freezer refrigerators are built to hold the cold with features like stainless steel handles that embody the heavy-duty strength Maytag is known for. The EVEN AIR cooling tower keeps food cool without breaking a sweat, while the POWER COLD feature chills down the refrigerator to help keep everything cool even if the whole family's been browsing with the door open. The electronic temperature controls are even up front to make maintaining the coolness of your refrigerator easy with the touch of a button. Plus, fingerprint resistant stainless steel keeps this fridges looking great. Inside this 21 cu. ft. top-freezer refrigerator you'll also find BRIGHT SERIES LED lighting. It casts a bright, white light and uses less energy than incandescent bulbs.
